Hi Natalie, 

Thanks and likewise!! 

Those changes are all straightforward. We recommend setting up a redirect. In short, if anyone visits the old URL, we redirect them to the new URL. 

This is best practice in the event someone has saved the old URL and avoids any negative SEO impact. 

We can organise a Zoom call to discuss the implications of name and URL and check what search phrases/keywords would be most relevant. You are welcome to choose your preferred time here: https://calendly.com/chris-paradowski/wolf-iq-introduction30min
